{"tid":2151633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"慷他人之慨系列：【賑災基金撥款近1千萬元　支援中國水災災民】","createTime":"2020-08-11T13:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T13:15:13.000Z","uid":329428,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fe02bd6b5d2a03ecab22ac7fb978d163915a0acb","tid":2151633,"uid":329428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:12:10.000Z","msg":"香港特別行政區政府接納賑災基金諮詢委員會的建議，從賑災基金批出兩項共9956000元的撥款，予兩間機構賑濟安徽省、貴州省、湖南省、江西省及雲南省水災災民。<br />\n <br />\n政府發言人今日（8月11日）表示，中國受水災影響的人數超過3700萬人。兩項撥款分別為5798000元予愛德基金會（香港）及4158000元予香港世界宣明會。撥款會用於提供食米、食油、棉被和家庭用品，約62200名災民受惠。委員會希望撥款能為災民提供適切援助，幫助他們早日回復正常生活。在計及上述及較早前就是次中國水災批出的撥款後，累計的撥款額及受惠人數分別為11056000元及74200。<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/08-11-2020/65362\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F08-11-2020%2F65362&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FreFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=ab4cf76f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/08-11-2020/65362</a>"},{"pid":"be292a54410a766c29054c8e2f85600ddf780ed4","tid":2151633,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc7f63a0935a3ed0c7a8f788e036359af6cb453","tid":2151633,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:13:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老母世界第二大經濟體"},{"pid":"194b013a1bfd615ee1ecfdedcd4661619388c9bc","tid":2151633,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:13:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10d6b2e6a6d837825b31ee869270c7899aa3397e","tid":2151633,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:13:29.000Z","msg":"泄露国家機密 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s